    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1911-06-16T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1911-06-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="137"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d137">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 437.00/9.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-06-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 16, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your telegram of June 8 received. President Gómez requests me to ascertain as
                    soon as practicable whether or not President Taft will act as arbitrator.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Jackson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
